A Perl library for Pine
=======================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module only requires one module not already available
in the standard Perl 5.8 distribution:

  File::Spec		# Cross-platform file names operations

However, if you wish to use the pinestats script, you will need to install:

  Tie::IxHash		# Ordered associative arrays
  Email::Address	# RFC 2822 address
  MIME::Words		# RFC 1522 encoded words


